  "detailed_description": "You will play one of the roles: wealthy heiress, office worker, and grandfather.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114310/extras/546836123c04ba7af190dab0ed0e26d1.avif?t=1731906998\" width=350 height=165 /></span><br><br>You will be hungry, you will be tired, you must persevere, live hard, and one day you can buy a luxurious house to ensure your life.<br><br>Start from a booth and grow vigorously!<br><br>You can choose different stall locations, sell different products, and earn different profits from different locations and products.<br><br>Don't forget to sleep, you can't do anything without energy!<br><br>All kinds of customers, buying and selling depend not only on the customers, but also on you. Do not attempt to deceive customers excessively<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114310/extras/9e10fcf70d6553b8a529ced1bb03a0a8.poster.avif?t=1731906998\" width=426 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114310/extras/9e10fcf70d6553b8a529ced1bb03a0a8.webm?t=1731906998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114310/extras/9e10fcf70d6553b8a529ced1bb03a0a8.mp4?t=1731906998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
